i go stupid

road to sweets 2

come join the gated collectors telegram chat after you grab this
[link in my pinned tweet]

prod by roho, thank you for everything

lyrics.text:
Aioli on my french fries
Y'all boys like that quick rise
Incentivized by potential to always hold it inside
Constantly televised on the go like a pedal bike
Hard but I'm soft on the inside like metal pipes
Fist covered in metal spikes
Carving out a vision for my mind is so Geppetto-like
My baby said that she don't fuck with men
I said I know you right
Precision that I shoot with be so deadly this a needle fight, Haku

Y'all boys are stupid
Yea stupid
I go stupid
Y'all look stupid
Okay I go stupid
Yeah stupid
Ok stupid, stupid, stupid, stupid

Lines of poetry I write for you inside my journal, I,
Miss you so, like misteletoe infrequently I see your smile,
Wonder how the wonder of the world is lost on us most times,
That’s human nature I guess,
That’s human nature I guess, so doom and gloom in abysses,
My mama so depressed with them awesome intentions,
I could see pain in all her inflections,
Insi the context of trauma reflected
Inside her fake smile and subdued gestures,
Some of these days I could sure use a lecture,
Or a fist made of iron to fix all my flaws,
It’s harder to hold her when everything falls,
The water from eyes leave me wetter than all,
Hell dawg how many times I done held her and said it’s alright when the pressure she under not fillin my eyes,
I understand that some wounds are not better w time,
The family tree we got it always tend to divide
But long as you know I'm always here and right on your side it's alright

Y'all boys are stupid
Yea stupid
I go stupid
Y'all look stupid
Okay I go stupid
Yeah stupid
Ok stupid, stupid, stupid, stupid
